io.com/bdsradiocharts/charts.aspx?formatid=53|title=BDS Dance/Mix Show Airplay Chart|work=Billboard|accessdate=March 4, 2020}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref name=\"US-HH\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/search?artistname=Doja+Cat&chartcode=BSI|title=Chart Search: Doja Cat - Hot R&B/Hip Hop Songs|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|access-date=March 31, 2020}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US [[Mainstream Top 40]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref name=\"Pop Songs\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/search?artistname=Doja+Cat&chartcode=TFM|title=Chart Search: Doja Cat, Mainstream Top 40|work=Billboard|accessdate=March 31, 2020}}</ref>\n| 10\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US [[Rhythmic (chart)|Rhythmic]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/search?artistname=Doja+Cat&chartcode=TFC|title=Chart Search: Doja Cat, Rhythmic Songs|work=Billboard|accessdate=March 31, 2020}}</ref>\n| 5\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US [[Rolling Stone Top 100|''Rolling Stone'' Top 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/charts/songs/2020-03-04/|title=Top 100 Songs|work=[[Rolling Stone]]|date=March 4, 2020|accessdate=March 4, 2020}}</ref>\n| 9\n|}\n\n==Certifications==\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Australia|type=single|award=Platinum|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|certref=<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=March 30, 2020|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=New Zealand|artist=Doja Cat|title=Say So|award=Gold|type=single|relyear=2019|relmonth=11|recent=website|id=4826|accessdate=February 29, 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|artist=Doja Cat|title=Say So|award=Silver|type=single|relyear=2019|certye