ition of Ireland}}\n| Ireland\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Baldwin, Dorothy\" | Dorothy Baldwin<ref name=\"GRG WSRL\"/>\n| align=center | F\n| 8 February 1902\n| 1 January 2014\n| England\n| England\n\n|-\n| 58\n| data-sort-value=\"Fewster\" | Mary Ann Fewster<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in the United Kingdom\"/>\n| align=center | F\n| 6 February 1878\n| 26 December 1989\n| {{ayd | 6 February 1878 | 26 December 1989}}\n| England\n| England\n\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 59\n| data-sort-value=\"Pannell\" | Florence Pannell<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in the United Kingdom\"/>\n| align=center | F\n| 26 December 1868\n| 20 October 1980\n| rowspan=2 | {{ayd | 26 December 1868 | 20 October 1980}}\n| England\n| England\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Kaufmann\" | Edith Kaufmann<ref name=\"GRG WSRL\"/>\n| align=center | F\n| 12 December 1903\n| 7 October 2015\n| nowrap | [[Austria-Hungary]]{{efn|Kaufmann was born in [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]], then part of Austria-Hungary, now in the [[Czech Republic]].}}\n| England\n\n|-\n| 61\n| data-sort-value=\"Hart\" | Rose Hart<ref name=\"Supercentenarians who lived in the United Kingdom\"/>\n| align=center | F\n| 20 March 1878\n| 5 January 1990\n| {{ayd | 20 March 1878 | 5 January 1990}}\n| England\n| England\n\n|-\n| 62\n| data-sort-value=\"Frampton\" | Ivy Frampton<ref name=\"GRG WSRL\"/>\n| align=center | F\n| 22 November 1903\n| 5 September 2015\n| {{ayd | 22 November 1903 | 5 September 2015}}\n| England\n| England\n\n|-\n| 63\n| data-sort-value=\"Steele\" | Elsie Steele<ref name=\"GRG Deaths in 2010\"/>\n| align=center | F\n| 6 January 1899\n| 18 October 2010\n| {{ayd | 6 January 1899 | 18 October 2010}}\n| England\n| England\n\n|-\n| 64\n| data-sort-value=\"Clulow\" | Hilda May Clulow<ref name=\"BBC News\">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/av/uk-england-hereford-worcester-47591721/super-hilda-celebrates-111th-birthday-in-redditch |title=Super Hilda celebrates 111th birthday |work=[[BBC News]] |date=16 March 2019 |access